if OS.mac?
  ### Rust (macOS) ###
  # Homebrew's rustup is code-signed — avoids macOS linker sandbox restrictions.
  # On Linux, install/rust.sh uses rustup-init directly (no Homebrew needed).
  brew "rustup"

